Program 2 - Simplified HTTP Retriever and Server  
Written By: Tom Petit <thopet@uw.edu>
CSS 432, Spring 2015

USAGE for retriever :
    bin/retriever address port
    ex: bin/retriever google.com/ 80

USAGE for HW2 server:
    bin/server port www_folder
    ex: bin/server 8080 www/

    www_folder is the path to the folder which is the web root. an example www/
    is provided.

demo.sh
    Runs the webserver in the background and supresses it's output.
    Then each test case is run and subsequently printed.

screenshots/
    for screenshots of successful tests, refer to the screenshots/ directory

A Makefile is provided for building. Tested on the lab machines and under OS X.

to build: make
to clean: make clean

Code revisioned in git.

